 ======================= README ======================= 

HOW TO RUN:
1. Clone the repository to our pc
2. After cloning review on it and can improve
3. Open index.html in browser
4. No backend needed (uses localStorage)
5. After improving add that to forked one repo by using "git add file_name" in terminal
6. git commit -m "something u want to give message to us can type here"
7. "git pull" and then "git push origin main" if origin is main otherwish "git push origin master".

ADVANCED IMPROVEMENTS YOU CAN ADD:
- Firebase backend
- Authentication system
- Real-time donor matching
- Location-based search
